module MiniC-ASTSyntax-testcases

language MiniC
start symbol Statement

test assignment [[x = 1;]] parse to Assignment(_, _)
test assignment [[x[0] = 1;]] parse to Assignment(_, _)
test assignment [[x.y = 1;]] parse to Assignment(_, _)
test if         [[if (x == 1) foo(); else bar();]] parse to IfElse(_,[_],[_])
test while      [[while (x == 1) foo();]] parse to While(_,[_])
test printf     [[printf("%i", x);]] parse to Printf([_],[_])
test block      [[{x = 1;}]] parse to Block([_])
